data.description: TAX ABATEMENT UNTIL 2026!! Stunning, fully-renovated single family home in the heart of Lakewood. This home is minutes away from all the entertainment and restaurants that Lakewood has to offer as well as the major highways making traveling anywhere convenient. The main level features extra tall ceilings, luxury vinyl throughout the entire level, a formal dining room, an oversized great room, powder room, and a gorgeous kitchen complete with 42” cabinets and a statement piece granite countertop. As you move up to the second level, you’ll find 3 spacious spare bedrooms and a full bathroom. You will also find the master bedroom with the Lakewood rarity ensuite bathroom complete with a freestanding soaker tub, shower and dual vanities. This entire home has been rejuvenated over the past 3 years and is move in ready for the next owner!
